task.summary: Started movement. Simplified PhysicalObject#nextPosition(). Cannot copy without either a concrete class or an abstract copy. Also, not worth it, as move only applies the velocity, accelerations are applied externally and others account for gravity. (namely the Area's pullDown methods)
Explosion on tank hit. Explosions on blocks also affect tanks.
Turn coloring and explosion color depend on player color.
Minor bug fix. Shell out of screen will now correctly change turn.
Impact impulse, air drag, and ground friction implemented as discussed with Ian.
Terrain block limits and bump debug.
Barrel drawing. This should be selectable from the start menu.
Moved the 'game' functionality to a screen. Also re-organized a lot of stuff.
Extracted createShellShape to its own method.
remove old 'g' variables that used to be 'Game instances'
